reason.tex:
%text
If $n$ is a \underline\text{positive integer} and $a,b\in\mathbb{R}$
then $(a+b)^n$ expands to the following
%
\begin{align}
 (a+b)^n &= {^n}C_0 a^n + {^n}C_1 a^{n-1}b^1 \\
 &+ {^n}C_2a^{n-2}b^2 + \ldots + {^n}C_na^{0}b^n \\
 &= \sum_{k=1}^n\,^{n}C_k\cdot a^{n-k}\cdot b^{k} 
\end{align}
